{"tid":1399162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史回顧 18年來首見意外感應光纖被撞斷　青馬大橋全封","createTime":"2019-08-03T05:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T12:28:54.000Z","uid":258731,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0d42026f51bcbb965a4dd0a1ddecf2b9766b5c30","tid":1399162,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:18:27.000Z","msg":"青嶼幹線發生通車18年來最嚴重的交通癱瘓事故，一艘躉船昨晚駛經汲水門大橋時懷疑與大橋碰撞，導致大橋感應器兩條光纖斷掉，響起防震警號，須緊急檢查。受事件影響，青馬大橋上下層行車線、港鐵機場快綫及東涌綫一度封閉。其間青嶼幹線塞滿車輛，交通完全癱瘓達兩小時，不僅市民有家歸不得，來往機場更無路可通，大批旅客被迫要去中環搭船往愉景灣及梅窩，再往機場，場面混亂。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20151024/19345961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20151024%2F19345961&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=035acfbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20151024%2F19345961&h=55e2e19e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20151024/19345961</a>"},{"pid":"31629d1eb8e328d11ddd2ed8604dba5a50d7ce25","tid":1399162,"uid":5499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:34:48.000Z","msg":"真正攬炒，首先你要有咁大隻船"},{"pid":"d4e2a5dc9c802c52ae7cb52a1ca400192d03f88f","tid":1399162,"uid":827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03e69d55c8916d56184e0918ca3c05cf01b637d","tid":1399162,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31629d1eb8e328d11ddd2ed8604dba5a50d7ce25","tid":1399162,"uid":5499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:34:48.000Z","msg":"真正攬炒，首先你要有咁大隻船"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:39:32.000Z","msg":"然後搵人揸船一野抄埋去"},{"pid":"e73c5eaf6c637a836b7d56d84fd8acb3134c59cf","tid":1399162,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2